José Antonio Fortea Cucurull (born in Barbastro, Spain, 1968), priest and specialized theologian in Demonology.
Author of several books about Demonology, demonic possession and exorcism, every year he gives lectures in dioceses and universities around the World.
He carries out his ministry of praying for persons afflicted by the Devil in Our Lady of Zulema Parish in the diocese of Alcalá de Henares (Madrid, Spain).
